    "description": "<p>Job Description:</p>\n\n<p>Pursuing quality of all SUSE products is one of our core beliefs. As a Software Engineer in Test you are here to push products to their limit, making sure they perform to customer expectations and conform to the highest quality standards. Using various kinds of programming and scripting languages in partnership with developers and project managers, you write test cases and plan, design, develop, and maintain automation tools to isolate and debug problems. The SUSE Quality Assurance department is distributed across the major engineering locations in Germany, the Czech Republic and China. We work in collaboration across teams and the SUSEorganization. Together we demand highest quality SUSE Linux products.</p>\n\n<p>Core Responsibilities:</p>\n\n<p>Develop and maintain the automation tools and various test scenarios\nInteract closely with release management, project management and development teams for a strong understanding of the project and of the testing objectives\nPrepare and deploy test environment\nDocument, track and escalate issues\nStay up to date with new testing tools and test strategies\nMaintain documentation\nWorking with openQA the leading automated solution for testing Linux distributions https://openqa.suse.de/</p>\n\n<p>Required Skills and Experience:</p>\n\n<p> at least 2 years of relevant experience as QA Automation Engineer\nexpertise in at least one of following scripting languages: Shell, Perl or Python\nfamiliarity with Linux administration\nworking knowledge of git\ngood communication skills and fluent in verbal and written English We are looking for self-motivated, creative and pro-active person eager to work with \"Free OpenSource software\"</p>\n\n<p>What we offer:</p>\n\n<p>Positive and creative work environment with an international team\nA growing business that is at the forefront of bringing new offerings to the Linux community\nDirect contact with representatives of free/open source software projects worldwide\nContributions to pension insurance or capital life insurance\nA competitive remuneration package</p>\n\n<p>About SUSE</p>\n\n<p>SUSE, a pioneer in open source software, provides reliable, software-defined infrastructure and application delivery solutions that give enterprises greater control and flexibility. More than 25 years of engineering excellence, exceptional service and an unrivaled partner ecosystem power the products and support that help our customers manage complexity, reduce cost, and confidently deliver mission-critical services. The lasting relationships we build allow us to adapt and deliver the smarter innovation they need to succeedótoday and tomorrow.</p>\n\n<p>For more information, visit www.suse.com</p>\n\n<p>Location:\nCzech Republic, Prague (CZPRG01)\nTracking code\n2018314\nPosition Type\nFull-Time/Regular</p>",
