    "location": "Bordeaux, France",
    "type": "Full Time",
    "description": "<p>At OneSpan, you’ll be part of a team that is trusted by more than 10,000 organizations around the world to safeguard their customers against cyber-crime and fraud, and deliver exceptional digital experiences that build lasting customer loyalty. Your contribution will help us to push the boundaries of what’s possible to improve the security and lives of millions of people around the world. In short, what you do here matters.</p>\n\n<p>OneSpan is looking for a ‘Quality Assurance Test Engineer ’ to join its R&amp;D department in Bordeaux.</p>\n\n<p>The ‘Quality Assurance Test Engineer’ has to assure the quality of software products and verify that the specifications are fulfilled.</p>\n\n<p>Responsibilities</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Development of test plans, test cases and test procedures.</li>\n<li>Execution of test plans in an efficient manner to ensure a quality product is delivered.</li>\n<li>Provide developers with appropriate level of information, analysis and demonstration.</li>\n<li>Proper reporting of found issues in the bug tracking system.</li>\n<li>Use and improvement of testing processes and procedures.</li>\n<li>Active participation in specification and user documentation reviews to find and resolve issues.</li>\n<li>Development and maintenance of the local test center</li>\n</ul><p>Profile</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>You have a Bachelor of Science in Computer Science or Engineering. </li>\n<li><p>You have a minimum of 2 years of experience in software testing. </p></li>\n<li><p>Required experience: \no You have experience in client-server / multi-tier application testing and web application testing. \no You have experience in structure testing methodology (including test design techniques).</p></li>\n<li><p>Assets: \no Knowledge in domain network and administration.\no Experience in Mobile Phone software technology. \no Knowledge of Java/C.</p></li>\n<li><p>You are able to work in a fast-paced, highly productive and rapidly changing environment.</p></li>\n<li><p>You have excellent analytical and communication skills.</p></li>\n<li><p>You are a fast learner with a hands-on mentality and a positive ‘can do’ attitude.</p></li>\n<li><p>You are creative and innovative, willing to try new things. </p></li>\n<li><p>You are fluent in French and English.</p></li>\n</ul>",
